A taxonomy classification application
====================================

The application implements a simple taxonomy classification system implemented as a multi-way tree
The current version is an implementation with Akka actors.

Models
======

v1 - TTree.scala
An implementation in a single file

v2 - Tree.scala, Taxonomy.scala, JsonFormatter.scala
An implementation based on a multi-way tree trait

v3 - TaxonomyActor.scala, TaxonomyNode.scala, TTag.scala
An implementation based on Akka actors

Tests
=====

v1 - TTreeSpec
v2 - TaxonomySpec
v3 - TaxonomyActorSpec

